Speciality of the Corner
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b Black to play\b0 .
\par The Black \'a1\'e3 stones and the White \'a1\'e2 stones are in a capturing race.
\par
\par White has four liberties, how many liberties Black has?
\par
\par If Black would have four liberties, the one who plays first can win the capturing race.
\par }
