Dia. 01 Easy Problem
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black could win the capturing race with 1, it would be a \cf1\b too easy problem\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par If Black plays dansu at 2, White connects at 3 and wins the capturing race.
\par
\par Black has four, while White has only three liberties.
\par
\par
\par }
