Dia. 02 Vital Point of the Capturing Race
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par The sequence in the previous diagram was bad.
\par After Black blocks at \'a1\'e3, White throws-in at 1. This is the vital point of the capturing race.
\par
\par Black has to take with 2 and then White can play dansu at 3. Black has to connect so \cf1\b White wins the capturing race\cf0\b0  with 5.
\par
\par }
