\par Black 1 is another mistake.
\par White's throw-in at 2 works again.
\par \cf1\b
\par Black fails \cf0\b0 with the sequence up to 6.
\par
\par Whenever White plays the throw-in move Black can't win the capturing race.
\par Then what can be the solution for Black?
\par
\par
\par
\par }
